Input Costs:

Image Input:


Lower tier: $0.00032875/image
Higher tier: $0.0006575/image


Video Input:


Lower tier: $0.00032875/second
Higher tier: $0.0006575/second


Text Input:


Lower tier: $0.0003125/1k characters
Higher tier: $0.000625/1k characters


Audio Input:


Lower tier: $0.00003125/second
Higher tier: $0.0000625/second

Output Costs:
Text Output:

Lower tier: $0.00125/1k characters
Higher tier: $0.0025/1k characters

For your PDF translation app workflow:

When scanning a PDF page with an image:

Image input cost: $0.00032875 (lower tier) per image
Output cost for extracted text: $0.00125 per 1k characters


For translation:

Text input cost: $0.0003125 per 1k characters
Output cost for translated text: $0.00125 per 1k characters



Example calculation for a single page PDF:
Let's say you have:

1 image to process
Extracted text is 2k characters
Translation generates 2k characters

Lower tier costs would be:

Image processing:

Input: $0.00032875
Output (2k chars): $0.0025


Translation:

Input (2k chars): $0.000625
Output (2k chars): $0.0025



Total cost: ~$0.005925 per page
